               class c - 197.10.10.0/24


               we require 5 networks (even b/w routers)



               197      10       10       0

               197      10      10        00000000     - network id

               2^n -2  >= 40
               2^6 -2  >= 40


               host bit -   0
               network bit - 1

               197     10      10       11000000

               197     10      10        192


  subnet mask   255   255    255     192


                197   10      10      0/26     subnet id1

                197   10      10      64/26    subnet id2

                197   10      10      128/26   subnet id3

